PN,41401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FThe Ashford MP, Sojan Joseph, has
OL,7,Fcriticised South East Water for what
OL,8,Fhe says are 'repeated failures'.
OL,10,FAround 4,000 of his constituents, who
OL,11,Fare South East Water customers, have
OL,12,Fbeen affected with either having no
OL,13,Fwater, shortages, or low pressure
OL,14,F(according to company's figures).
OL,16,FHe says he has "lost all faith" in the
OL,17,Fcompany due to repeated failures to
OL,18,Fdeliver basic standards of customer
OL,19,Fservice.
OL,26,@xD@POUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FHe's written to the Department for
OL,7,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs,
OL,8,Fasking the Secretary of State, Emma
OL,9,FReynolds MP, to take action.
OL,11,FSojan Joseph, MP for Ashford, Hawkinge
OL,12,Fand the Villages said "I have
OL,13,Fcompletely lost faith in South East
OL,14,FWater ` they have repeatedly failed to
OL,15,Fimprove standards for customers in my
OL,16,Fconstituency and across Kent.
OL,26,@tD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FSouth East Water have not invested in
OL,7,Fthe necessary infrastructure and, as a
OL,8,Fresult, have failed to ensure they do
OL,9,Fnot face shortages at times of high
OL,10,Fdemand ` this time just after a couple
OL,11,Fof days of warm weather.
OL,13,FI completely understand the
OL,14,Ffrustration of residents. I have
OL,15,Fwritten to DEFRA to ask the Secretary
OL,16,Fof State to take action and have been
OL,17,Fmaintaining contact with South East
OL,18,FWater on behalf of my constituents to
OL,19,Fstay on top of the detail.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FI am pleased the Government has taken
OL,7,Fsteps, such as the Water Act and the
OL,8,Fnew White Paper, to improve the
OL,9,Fstandards of water; however, this will
OL,10,Ftake time to come into effect."
OL,12,FThe MP's letter to the Department for
OL,13,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs,
OL,14,Freads;
OL,16,FI hope this letter finds you well.
OL,26,@rD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FI am writing to you on behalf of the
OL,7,Fresidents across Kent, including the
OL,8,F4,000 constituents of mine, who have
OL,9,Fbeen facing an ongoing water shortage
OL,10,Fdue to South East Water to ask your
OL,11,FDepartment to take action through
OL,12,Fcoordinated efforts with OFWAT, the
OL,13,FEnvironment Agency, and local
OL,14,Fauthorities to assist my constituents
OL,15,Fwho either have had no water, are
OL,16,Ffacing shortages, or low water
OL,17,Fpressure for just under a week ` which
OL,18,FSouth East Water are reporting is down
OL,19,Fto increased usage during this
OL,20,Fheatwave. I find this especially
OL,21,Fconcerning as we are not even in the
OL,22,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FThis more recent issue, faced by many
OL,7,Fof my constituents, is on top of the
OL,8,Fproblems faced by wider Kent
OL,9,Fresidents, such as those in Tunbridge
OL,10,FWells who were out of water for weeks
OL,11,Fover last winter. As a result
OL,12,Fresidents there have been forced to
OL,13,Feither use boiled or bottled water and
OL,14,Fhave been unable to perform basic
OL,15,Ftasks, such as washing or flushing
OL,16,Ftoilets. As I am sure you are aware
OL,17,Fthe issues in Tunbridge Wells,
OL,18,Feventually led to the resignation of
OL,19,FSouth East Water's then-CEO.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FResidents across Kent have gone
OL,7,Fwithout basic essentials, such as
OL,8,Fclean drinking water and the ability
OL,9,Fto bathe and wash due to South East
OL,10,FWater's inadequate service ` on top of
OL,11,Fthis their representatives have
OL,12,Fconsistently failed to communicate
OL,13,Fclearly to customers, local
OL,14,Fauthorities, and to Members of
OL,15,FParliament representing constituencies
OL,16,Fthroughout the county, which has
OL,17,Ffurther slowed-down the process of
OL,18,Fresolving the issue and eventual
OL,19,Faccountability.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FWhilst, I know the Government's
OL,7,Fmeasures such as the new Water Act and
OL,8,Fthe 'A New Vision for Water' white
OL,9,Fpaper will hugely improve standards in
OL,10,Fthe long-term, many of constituents
OL,11,Fare struggling now, and as a result
OL,12,Fthey and I have lost all faith in
OL,13,FSouth East Water's ability to deliver
OL,14,Fthe basic standards a provider should
OL,15,Fbe able to give to their customers.
OL,17,FThank you for taking the time to read
OL,18,Fthis letter and I look forward to
OL,19,Freading your response.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FAt the height of this week's water
OL,7,Fsupply issues, more than 18,000 people
OL,8,Fin Kent and Sussex have been affected.
OL,10,FDuring a heatwave when temperatures
OL,11,Freached 30 C and above during
OL,12,Fconsistent days, South East Water
OL,13,Fcustomers have had to reply on bottled
OL,14,Fsupplies.
OL,16,FToday (Saturday 30 May), the company
OL,17,Fsays drinking water supplies have been
OL,18,Frestored for 15,000 of its customers
OL,19,Facross Kent, including those in
OL,20,FWhitstable and Herne Bay areas.
OL,26,@sD@LOX
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FSouth East Water's Incident Manager,
OL,7,FSteve Benton, said "Whilst this is
OL,8,Fpositive, we are conscious that today
OL,9,Fis forecast to be another hot day and
OL,10,Fdemand is therefore likely to remain
OL,11,Fhigh.
OL,13,FAlthough our network is recovering,
OL,14,Flevels of drinking water in our
OL,15,Fstorage tanks are still low and we are
OL,16,Fasking customers to use water for
OL,17,Fessential purposes only - drinking,
OL,18,Fcooking, and hygiene. We are
OL,19,Fcontinuing to use our tankers to
OL,20,Fsupport the network and aid recovery.
OL,26,@oD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FWe are working hard to restore
OL,7,Fsupplies to around 500 customers
OL,8,Facross Kent who are currently without
OL,9,Fwater. This includes around 165
OL,10,Fcustomers in Cranbrook, fewer than 20
OL,11,Fin Ulcombe, and 111 in Mereworth. This
OL,12,Fis because the drinking water storage
OL,13,Ftanks which serve these areas have
OL,14,Freached a critical level.
OL,16,FWe're also working to repair a burst
OL,17,Fwater main impacting around 182
OL,18,Fcustomers in Brook, Ashford.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FIn addition, there are approximately
OL,7,F3000 customers who may be experiencing
OL,8,Flow pressure or an intermittent supply
OL,9,Fin the Coxheath, Loose, Headcorn,
OL,10,FUlcombe, Kemsing and Benenden areas.
OL,12,FWe are sincerely sorry to customers
OL,13,Ffor disruption to their water supply
OL,14,Fand know how frustrating it is,
OL,15,Fespecially in hot weather.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FWhile tap water supplies have returned
OL,7,Ffor most customers who have been
OL,8,Fimpacted across Kent, some may still
OL,9,Fexperience water supply issues as a
OL,10,Fresult of the incredibly high demand
OL,11,Fduring this heatwave.
OL,13,FFor the majority of customers still
OL,14,Fimpacted, tap water may be
OL,15,Fintermittent, with water going on and
OL,16,Foff throughout the day, with no water
OL,17,For low pressure at peak times,
OL,18,Fparticularly between 7am to 9am and
OL,19,F4pm to 7pm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FWe are doing everything we can to get
OL,7,Ftreated water into our drinking water
OL,8,Fstorage tanks, including using our
OL,9,Ftankers to support the network and
OL,10,Fensuring all available treatment works
OL,11,Fare running at full capacity.
OL,13,FIn areas where there has been a supply
OL,14,Finterruption - or where we believe
OL,15,Fissues may occur - we're delivering
OL,16,Fbottled water to customers on our
OL,17,FPriority Services Register.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FWe have delivered more than 230,000
OL,7,Flitres of water to customers on our
OL,8,FPriority Services Register and also
OL,9,Fdelivered bottled water to critical
OL,10,Fcare settings such as care homes, GP
OL,11,Fsurgeries, pharmacies and dentists.
OL,13,FWe have been working 24/7 with our
OL,14,Ffleet of tankers to support our
OL,15,Fnetwork where demand has been
OL,16,Fextremely high. So far, we have
OL,17,Ftankered over 2,025,700 litres of
OL,18,Fwater into the network.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FWe have also given out almost 900,000
OL,7,Flitres of water at our bottled water
OL,8,Fstations across Kent and continue to
OL,9,Fidentify new locations for other
OL,10,Fstations to open.
OL,12,FAdditionally, we are supporting the
OL,13,FQueen Victoria Memorial Hospital in
OL,14,FHerne Bay and an urgent care unit with
OL,15,Fa tanker and supporting those with
OL,16,Flivestock.
OL,18,FWe are continuing to ask customers in
OL,19,Fsupply to use water for essential
OL,20,Fpurposes only - for example drinking,
OL,21,Fcooking and hygiene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780153874
OL,3,CMP says he's 'lost all faith' in water
OL,4,Ccompany
OL,6,FOur call centre is experiencing high
OL,7,Fcall volumes. Customers can find FAQs,
OL,8,Fdetails of bottled water stations and
OL,9,Finformation about locations currently
OL,10,Fexperiencing supply issues via our
OL,11,Fwebsite.
OL,13,FWe will continue to do all we can to
OL,14,Fprevent and resolve the issues".
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G17/17
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
